<view class="page login-page">
  <view class="login-hero">
    <view class="login-badge">信息学院</view>
    <view class="login-title">学生综合服务与党团管理平台</view>
    <view class="login-subtitle">请登录后使用政策问答、党团流程、理论自测和管理员维护功能。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="login-panel card">
    <view class="login-tabs">
      <view class="login-tab {{passwordTabClass}}" data-mode="password" bindtap="switchMode">账号登录</view>
      <view class="login-tab {{registerTabClass}}" data-mode="register" bindtap="switchMode">注册账号</view>
    </view>

    <view wx:if="{{showPasswordLogin}}" class="password-login">
      <view class="form-row">
        <text class="form-label">账号</text>
        <input class="form-input" value="{{accountName}}" maxlength="32" placeholder="请输入已注册账号" bindinput="onAccountNameInput" />
      </view>
      <view class="form-row">
        <text class="form-label">密码</text>
        <input class="form-input" value="{{password}}" password placeholder="请输入密码" bindinput="onPasswordInput" />
      </view>
      <button class="primary-button full-button" bindtap="handlePasswordLogin">登录</button>
      <button class="secondary-button full-button" wx:if="{{showDemoEntry}}" bindtap="enterDemo">演示模式进入</button>
    </view>

    <view wx:if="{{showRegister}}" class="register-login">
      <view class="form-row">
        <text class="form-label">账号</text>
        <input class="form-input" value="{{registerAccountName}}" maxlength="32" placeholder="4-32 位字母、数字或下划线" bindinput="onRegisterAccountNameInput" />
      </view>
      <view class="form-row">
        <text class="form-label">昵称</text>
        <input class="form-input" value="{{displayName}}" maxlength="64" placeholder="可选，绑定后显示学生姓名" bindinput="onDisplayNameInput" />
      </view>
      <view class="form-row">
        <text class="form-label">密码</text>
        <input class="form-input" value="{{registerPassword}}" password placeholder="请输入 8-64 位密码" bindinput="onRegisterPasswordInput" />
      </view>
      <view class="form-row">
        <text class="form-label">确认密码</text>
        <input class="form-input" value="{{confirmPassword}}" password placeholder="请再次输入密码" bindinput="onConfirmPasswordInput" />
      </view>
      <button class="primary-button full-button" bindtap="handleRegister">注册并绑定学生信息</button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="login-note card">
    未注册账号需先注册并绑定本人学号和姓名。已注册账号可直接使用密码登录，暂不提供找回密码功能。
  </view>
</view>
